summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning, amending Plat 75W, page 177 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone the property located at 4518 Southwest Wildwood Place from Single Family 5000 (SF5000) to Lowrise Duplex-Triplex (LDT) and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of Linda C. Warehime, C.F. 299299)
committee: Housing, Community Development and Urban Environment
